pageContext.description: Length: 107.5mm; Width edge 60.5mm; Width mouth 41.5mm; Width loop 11.5mm; Breadth mouth 41mm; Depth socket 80mm,Obverse face with three thick ribs skewed and seperated by furrows; reverse ribs not well defined but prob. similar skew; irregular jet stumps at mouth; remains of fine casting flash; blade tip hollows - marked; few hammermarks on lower blade.
pageContext.patina: Dark brown-gold patina; substantial areas obscured by granular and lumpy lighter green surface
pageContext.surface: Part of edge good and fairly sharp, part lost through corrosion; few recent scratches at edge. Fawn and light orange-brown soil adhering.
